OL,3,CBusinesses fear free parking ban could
OL,4,Cforce them to shut shop
OL,6,FBusiness owners in a historic town in
OL,7,FEast Yorkshire say they may have to
OL,8,Fshut down if plans to scrap free
OL,9,Fparking go ahead.
OL,11,FEast Riding Council is considering
OL,12,Fintroducing charges across a number of
OL,13,Fareas which currently have free
OL,14,Fspaces, including Hessle.
OL,16,FRichard Skelton used to own a family
OL,17,Fchain of cake shops, but was forced to
OL,18,Fclose down almost all the branches
OL,19,Fafter parking charges were introduced
OL,20,Fnearby.
