OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "We used to have a
OL,7,Fshop on every corner, now we just have
OL,8,Fone.
OL,10,F"(Hessle) is our home now. It's where
OL,11,Fwe do everything and we want to
OL,12,Fprotect it.
OL,14,F"There's independent shops here and
OL,15,Fthey need help."
OL,17,FA petition set up by the town's mayor
OL,18,Fto oppose the plans has already
OL,19,Freached thousands of signatures.
