OL,3,CBusinesses fear free parking ban could
OL,4,Cforce them to shut shop
OL,6,FCllr Steven Craggs said: "You look
OL,7,Faround today and there's not one
OL,8,Fvacancy, not one premises available.
OL,9,FThat's how much the businesses mean to
OL,10,FHessle.
OL,12,F"When there's a rumour going round
OL,13,Fthat they would introduce charges -
OL,14,Fthis would probably end up a ghost
OL,15,Ftown."
OL,17,FEast Riding Council owns 64 car parks.
OL,18,FIts 8,000 spaces make around #4million
OL,19,Fa year.
